README:
This is the functional and structural MRI data used for the following studies:
```
Hamm, A.G. and Mattfeld, A. T. (2019) Distinct Neural Circuits Underlie Prospective
and Concurrent Memory-Guided Behavior, Cell Reports, Vol. 28(10)
```
Formerly ```https://openneuro.org/datasets/ds002078```

Folders are organised in subject number (e.g. sub-001). Within each folder there are subfolders with the following:

1) anat - T1-weighted structural scan

2) func - contains BOLD data for:
```
Our novel conditional visual associative learning task, with kaleidoscopic images used as stimuli with 6 scans across three sets of images. 
```

Please note that not all participants finished all tasks, or scans. See papers for a description.

sub-027_task-condassoc_run-02_events.jso.duration: Duration of trial from stimulus onset to end of ITI
sub-027_task-condassoc_run-02_events.jso.trial_type: Type of Trial, with A being Fixed Left, B being Conditional, and C being Fixed Right
sub-027_task-condassoc_run-02_events.jso.response_time: Amount of time it took subject to give left or right response in seconds (s)
sub-027_task-condassoc_run-02_events.jso.correct/incorrect: Whether subject got response correct or incorrect (1 = Correct, 0 = Incorrect)
